We went here to be able to watch the Bears game and the Packers game one sunday.
They found us a seat and made sure we could see both games.
The food was decent and the service was ok.
It is a good place to go if you want to watch multiple games at once.
I wouldn't go there all the time and it won't become my favorite hangout but I'd go back.

